node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Matthew Patrick on June 21, 2021 tagging @heyheyolliej. May be an image of 1 person, standing, sitting, outdoors and castle.

node.text:
It's guys like you, Mickey... That make it so incredibly fun to be a dad! Happy father's day to all the cool dads, the funny dads, the Disney dads, the dads who are grandpas, the dads who aren't being recognized as dads, the dads who can't be with their families this year, and for the dads we miss in our lives. I'm grateful for mine and hope to be the kind of dad my son is willing to take photos with for a few more years...

#fathersday
#disneyworld
#dadpat

Passing on a family tradition.

This is was officially Ollie's first "Big Kid" sledding experience with me and his grandpa. He LOVED it. So much so that after one run, he wanted to do it by himself. 

Also...that red sled is from when I was a kid. So REALLY passing on the tradition.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Matthew Patrick on February 26, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and eyeglasses.

node.text:
I'm partnering with @dollarshaveclub as part of their #mengetreal #ad campaign to share that it's ok for men to be vulnerable. 

So...this is a picture that has never seen the light of day (outside of my school yearbook 😱). Meet high school freshman MatPat. Yes, those are braces. Yes, that is a gold necklace. Yes, that is an unshaven mustache and HEAVY unibrow. In middle school and early high school, I REFUSED to shave those off because I thought they made me unique. I thought grooming those things away was me being ASHAMED of who I was. But that's not true. What I grew to understand was that what made me unique was on the inside, and no amount of shaving or personal grooming would take that away. And by taking care of my outside better, I could be stronger, more confident, and grow to love myself more without sacrificing my identity. 

So, if your unibrow needs grooming (or you have any other personal care needs) Dollar Shave Club has got you covered now at a store near you. Gold chain not included #dollarshaveclub
